{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-people-page-js","path":"/speakers/carlos-silva","result":{"data":{"people":{"parent":{"html":"<h2>About</h2>\n<p>Dr. Carlos Silva leads <a href=\"https://pachama.com/\">Pachama’s</a> Science Team. He guides the company’s efforts to integrate satellite observations into a platform for scalable, high-quality forest carbon crediting. He holds a PhD in remote sensing and global ecology, and previously worked on the science team of NASA’s GEDI mission, which measures forest structure globally. He also holds a master's degree in economics and public policy, and has developed forest carbon projects for both the voluntary and compliance markets.</p>"},"id":"ab8a0642-c8bf-56fd-8be8-5ac4b5d5482c","title":"Carlos Silva, PhD","company":"Pachama","role":"Science Team Lead","twitter":"carlos_pachama","pronouns":null,"avatar":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/7096585f0ac31a28110fb6cc165ab1c7/1b50a/carlos-silva.jpg","srcSet":"/static/7096585f0ac31a28110fb6cc165ab1c7/c904d/carlos-silva.jpg 160w,\n/static/7096585f0ac31a28110fb6cc165ab1c7/b95ad/carlos-silva.jpg 320w,\n/static/7096585f0ac31a28110fb6cc165ab1c7/1b50a/carlos-silva.jpg 640w","sizes":"(min-width: 640px) 640px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/7096585f0ac31a28110fb6cc165ab1c7/c6aca/carlos-silva.webp 160w,\n/static/7096585f0ac31a28110fb6cc165ab1c7/0a0af/carlos-silva.webp 320w,\n/static/7096585f0ac31a28110fb6cc165ab1c7/8ae69/carlos-silva.webp 640w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 640px) 640px, 100vw"}]},"width":640,"height":640}}},"events":[{"role":"speakers","event":{"parent":{"html":"<p>Several big bets have been made on the ability of satellite data to improve carbon accounting. This panel will explore what is required for meaningful carbon accounting, where better earth data and better models will contribute, and what are their limitations.</p>"